-----
  
🔹 Login & Project
oc login https://api.<cluster-domain>:6443
oc project studentX
oc whoami

🔹 Deploy Application (Imperative)
oc create deployment loan-app --image=nginxinc/nginx-unprivileged

  🔹 Scale Application
oc scale deployment loan-app --replicas=3

  🔹 Expose Application
oc expose deployment loan-app --port=8080 --target-port=8080
oc expose svc loan-app

  🔹 Check Resources
oc get pods
oc get svc
oc get route
oc get all

🔹 View Logs & Debug
oc logs <pod-name>
oc describe pod <pod-name>

🔹 Declarative Deployment
oc apply -f app.yaml
oc delete -f app.yaml

🔹 ConfigMap & Secret
oc create configmap app-config --from-literal=ENV=dev
oc create secret generic app-secret --from-literal=PASSWORD=123

  🔹 Cleanup (IMPORTANT)
oc delete all --all
oc delete configmap --all
oc delete secret --all


